      <title>财政部长为何关注 10 年期国债收益率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/why-10-year-yields-are-on-the-treasury-secretary-s-mind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融新闻中总是充斥着数字，但有一个数字几乎总是比其他任何数字都重要：10 年期美国国债收益率，这是帮助为全球数万亿美元资产定价的重要基准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/why-10-year-yields-are-on-the-treasury-secretary-s-mind</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 16:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
